    GenericFormat

    public class HOG2Map
extends java.lang.Object
implements GenericFormat
    Class that implements a HOG2 repository HOG2Map file format parser. Repository is available at: http://www.movingai.com/benchmarks/index.html
    Author:
    G. Amador & A. Gomes
